<view class="container">
  <view class="section-title">📈 图表生成器</view>
  <view class="placeholder-content">
    <text class="placeholder-text">图表生成器开发中...</text>
    <text class="placeholder-desc">支持柱状图、饼图、折线图等多种图表类型

即将推出功能：
• 拖拽式图表配置
• 实时数据绑定
• 多种图表样式
• 一键导出图片
• 响应式设计适配</text>
  </view>
  
  <!-- 基础图表预览 -->
  <view class="chart-preview">
    <view class="preview-title">示例预览</view>
    <view class="sample-charts">
      <view class="sample-item">
        <text class="chart-type">柱状图</text>
        <view class="chart-demo bar-chart">
          <view class="bar" style="height: 60%;"></view>
          <view class="bar" style="height: 80%;"></view>
          <view class="bar" style="height: 45%;"></view>
          <view class="bar" style="height: 90%;"></view>
          <view class="bar" style="height: 70%;"></view>
        </view>
      </view>
      
      <view class="sample-item">
        <text class="chart-type">饼图</text>
        <view class="chart-demo pie-chart">
          <view class="pie-slice slice1"></view>
          <view class="pie-slice slice2"></view>
          <view class="pie-slice slice3"></view>
          <view class="pie-center"></view>
        </view>
      </view>
      
      <view class="sample-item">
        <text class="chart-type">折线图</text>
        <view class="chart-demo line-chart">
          <canvas canvas-id="sampleLine" class="line-canvas"></canvas>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>